        interface  TYPE seoitfname,

ty_implementations TYPE SORTED TABLE OF ty_implementation WITH NON-UNIQUE KEY interface

        interface TYPE seoitfname,
        filters   TYPE ty_filters,
        object    TYPE REF TO object,
      END OF ty_instance
ty_instances TYPE SORTED TABLE OF ty_instance WITH NON-UNIQUE KEY interface
